### Array

```php
<?php
$muuttuja = array(
    "yksi"  => 1,
    "kaksi" => 2
);

echo $muuttuja["yksi"];
?>
```

### Oliot

```php
<?php
class KUKKA {
  private $sana;

  function __construct() {
    $this->sana = "Neilikka";
  }

  public function sano() {
    echo $this->sana."\n";
  }
}

$olio = new KUKKA;
$olio->sano();
?>
```

